    "created_at": "2017-04-26T01:42:08Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-26T01:42:17Z",
    "body": "@Klestofer I think you are confused between the HTML5 Notification spec and Chromium's implementation of their Notification UI.  The current implementation of `Notification` inside Electrons renderer processes already follows a large portion of the HTML5 Notification spec but the UI is implemented through system notifications.\r\n\r\nFrom my own research macOS and W10 support a prop on their notifications to persist the notification until user interaction W7, W8 and LibNotify (linux) do not support this concept."
  },
